      <h1>Privacy Policy – NovaFlow (Premium Launcher)</h1>
      <div class="muted">Last updated: February 2026</div>

      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>NovaFlow ("we", "our", or "the app") is a premium Android launcher application. This Privacy Policy explains how NovaFlow handles information when you use the app. By installing or using NovaFlow, you agree to this Privacy Policy.</p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <h3>2.1 Information Stored Locally on Your Device</h3>
      <p>The following data is stored <b>only on your device</b> and is <b>not transmitted to our servers</b>:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>App preferences (favorites, hidden apps, layout, themes, fonts, wallpapers).</li>
        <li>PIN and app lock settings (stored locally and not accessible by us).</li>
        <li>Calendar data (if permission is granted).</li>
        <li>Notification content (if notification access is enabled).</li>
        <li>Installed app list (used only to display apps in the launcher).</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2.2 Information We Do NOT Collect</h3>
      <p>NovaFlow does not collect or store on external servers:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Name, email address (unless you contact support), phone number</li>
        <li>Contacts, messages, call logs</li>
        <li>Precise location data</li>
        <li>Advertising ID or analytics tracking data</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or share user data.</p>

      <h2>3. Permissions Used</h2>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Permission</th><th>Purpose</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Internet</td><td>Weather widget and optional online services</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Location</td><td>To provide weather information (if enabled by user)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Calendar (Read/Write)</td><td>To display and create events in the launcher</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Notification Access</td><td>To display notifications within the launcher</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Storage / Wallpaper</td><td>To set and manage wallpapers</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Other system permissions</td><td>Required for launcher functionality</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>You may revoke permissions at any time in system settings.</p>

      <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><b>Google Play</b> (for distribution and payments). We do not receive payment details.</li>
        <li><b>Weather API provider</b> (to fetch weather, if you use that feature).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>All locally stored data is protected by Android system security mechanisms. You can remove stored data by uninstalling NovaFlow or clearing app data.</p>

      <h2>6. Children’s Privacy</h2>
      <p>NovaFlow is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may revoke permissions at any time, disable notification access, uninstall the app, or contact us regarding privacy concerns. Users in the EEA/UK may have additional rights under GDPR.</p>

      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy when necessary. Updates will be posted on this page and/or in the store listing.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:bilal.2000088@gmail.com">bilal.2000088@gmail.com</a></p>
